
This Code made for Get Sentiment Analysis from Indonesia Tweet/Text.

2 Method used :
1. Neural Network with MLPClassifier
2. LSTM

The data for source :
1. Training : https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RCHGfn9JJyyReAh8PIIoF8Ch0H3miP0u/view?usp=sharing
2. Testing : https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ilhamfp31/indonesian-abusive-and-hate-speech-twitter-text.

Using Swagger UI to documented the api, flask as framework, python(pandas and regex) to cleansing, NLTK indonesia for stopwords removal and sqlite as database.
The api input can be text or file uploaded with extension csv.
The API method use here is POST.

